  "response": "Bruce Wayne is a fictional character from DC Comics, best known as the alter ego of Batman. He is a wealthy business magnate, philanthropist, and owner of Wayne Enterprises in Gotham City. After witnessing the murder of his parents as a child, he dedicates his life to battling crime and injustice, transforming himself into the vigilante superhero Batman. Using advanced technology, intellect, physical prowess, and detective skills, Bruce Wayne fights against various villains to protect Gotham City.",
